        "can_view_edit_history": true,
        "can_wiki": false,
        "cooked": "<p>In OpenSCAD (not the parametric model maker\u2013yet) you can use include if you specify a relative path. No need for a python script. I use this feature pretty often.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/OpenSCAD_User_Manual/Include_Statement\" class=\"onebox\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/OpenSCAD_User_Manual/Include_Statement</a></p>",
